era().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage and world

getNewSettlementCost(uint256).details: Calculates cost of placing new settlement in tokens

params.timestamp: Time at which calculate new settlement cost. If timestamp=0 -> calculates as block.timestamp

returns._0: Amount of tokens new settlement will cost

params.initParams: Encoded init params (every world asset has own knowledge how to extract data from it)

updateState().details: Called on every action which are based on settlement market state

world().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage

marketCreationTime.details: Immutable, initialized on the market creation

relatedRegion.details: Immutable, initialized on the market creation

OnlyActiveGame().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called in active game (started and not finished)

OnlyMightyCreator().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by mighty creator

OnlyWorldAssetFromSameEra().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by world asset from same era

ReentrantCall().notice: Thrown when attempting to call function via reentrancy

SettlementCannotBeBoughtDueInsufficientV.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement due to insufficient value sent (only if world.erc20ForSettlementPurchase == address(0), which is equivalent of native token)

SettlementCannotBeBoughtDueToCostIsHighe.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement due to new settlement cost is higher than max tokens to use specified

SettlementCannotBeBoughtForFreeAfterGame.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement for free by mighty creator after game began

SettlementCannotBeBoughtForNotOwnerBanne.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement for specified banner nft id and not owning it

SettlementCannotBeBoughtOnNonExistentPos.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement on non existent position

SettlementCannotBeBoughtOnPositionWhichI.notice: Thrown when attempting to buy settlement on position which is not related to this settlement market

UnknownInputParameter().notice: Thrown when attempting to call function by providing unknown parameter

getNewSettlementCost(uint256).notice: Returns amount of tokens new settlement will cost

marketCreationTime().notice: Time at which market was created

relatedRegion().notice: Region to which this market belongs

updateState().notice: Updates settlement market state to the current block

worldAssetFactory().notice: Returns world asset factory from registry
